    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014totally mint! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it polished and pristine. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
