    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, maintaining a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero stone chips. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car essence. Every switch, button, and electronic system operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting its pampered life. This turn-key example comes complete with all original manuals, both master keys, and the original window sticker. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark-quality vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
