      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in showroom condition and reflecting the highest standards of automotive preservation. The vehicle features a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade offering for the discerning buyer who prioritizes uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity. A rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of this caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
