    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! It's super reliable and ready for your next adventure. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
