    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a benchmark in longitudinal front-engine, rear-drive engineering. The S54B32 power unit remains a masterpiece of high-revving aspiration, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. This specific chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and treated rod bearings to ensure structural and mechanical integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a meticulously maintained M-Variable Differential Lock. The exterior finish is flawless, preserving the factory aerodynamics and flared wheel arches. Suspension geometry remains true, with bushings and dampers providing the precise feedback expected of a low-mileage, collector-grade specimen.",
